{"tid":2321962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：梁頌恆身處美國　將申請政治庇護　指在港一直被跟蹤","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:37:52.000Z","uid":290404,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7c3cc81a0ffc50e5a93c74d84b5e37647f5110","tid":2321962,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564933-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564933-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=88efc0c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564933-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b6574cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564933-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>因宣誓風波被褫奪立法會議員資格的梁頌恆</strong>表示，正身處美國華盛頓，將會申請政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆<strong>早前因參與非法集結罪成，今年9月初上訴被駁回後即時入獄4星期。</strong>他今早在網上記者會<strong>聲稱，自出獄後一直被人跟蹤，擔心自身安全得不到保障，所以決定離港。</strong><br />\n<br />\n他說是於11月30日離港，離港時沒有被阻止，目前居住於當地港人家中，已經安頓好，選擇到美國是基於分工考慮，因目前沒有很多政治人物到當地。<br />\n<br />\n被問到在美國將有何計劃，梁頌恆說，會推動「救生艇計劃」，協助有需要港人前往美國尋求庇護，以及推動美方調整制裁中國的方案，例如考慮制裁香港金融，並已聯絡美國國會議員等人士見面。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆說，在港已沒有與他有關連的刑事案件，早前就參與非法集結罪上訴至終審法院，亦已申請不用上庭，律師會繼續處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前被裁定要全數向立法會交還薪津及訟費，梁頌恆表示，估計兩者合共約500多萬元，但不打算處理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>由於梁頌恆無理會立法會的追討，行管會之前已向法院申請他破產，案件原定於本月初聆訊。</strong>"},{"pid":"514bd10482f7e826a6f78214446f11cab75dfd1c","tid":2321962,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"因宣誓風波被褫奪立法會議員資格的梁頌恆<br />\n因恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9b3100085e69667601fda1abb752e48d2187fb","tid":2321962,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"514bd10482f7e826a6f78214446f11cab75dfd1c","tid":2321962,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"因宣誓風波被褫奪立法會議員資格的梁頌恆<br />\n因恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"冇成本又可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005d13d91751f52b9e05d244fedf7851499a3e44","tid":2321962,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"514bd10482f7e826a6f78214446f11cab75dfd1c","tid":2321962,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"因宣誓風波被褫奪立法會議員資格的梁頌恆<br />\n因恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"擺明係編輯想幫政府醜化梁頌恆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f966dd14d1338d2c5d77f309c9ba22491ed92d5","tid":2321962,"uid":41853,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7d9b3100085e69667601fda1abb752e48d2187fb","tid":2321962,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"514bd10482f7e826a6f78214446f11cab75dfd1c","tid":2321962,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"因宣誓風波被褫奪立法會議員資格的梁頌恆<br />\n因恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"冇成本又可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"佢好似欠立會成百萬，所以先走佬喎<br />\n<br />\n似走數多過似尋求政治庇護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b897222a41cd7717ef181b595565d74d021f0e","tid":2321962,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f966dd14d1338d2c5d77f309c9ba22491ed92d5","tid":2321962,"uid":41853,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7d9b3100085e69667601fda1